  "text": "By accessing the Immunology Database and Analysis Portal (IMMPORT) [CITATION_1] website (https://www. immport.org), we retrieved a latest list of immune-related genes, out of which we identified BLCA-specific immune-related genes (IRGs) after matching the DEGs. Survival-associated IRGs were identified using univariate Cox regression analysis with a threshold value of p < 0.01.",
